  "replies_posted": [
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/CPTheFanchise/status/2036781591075213654",
      "reply_text": "Yeah 7 in a row is nice but playoffs are a different beast. See how they adapt.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T12:45:03.932197+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/LukaDoncicStanD/status/2036776139671138550",
      "reply_text": "Not sure what games you've been watching, but Luka's numbers don't lie.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T12:45:53.334736+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/923TheFan/status/2036765609015365966",
      "reply_text": "Yeah expectations are good, but it's a tough road to the Finals.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T12:46:42.528002+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BradeauxNBA/status/2036786296228561297",
      "reply_text": "Both teams are fighting for home court in the playoffs.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T12:59:30.825211+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/bballforever_/status/2036782651072487684",
      "reply_text": "Wichita State and Oklahoma highlights. What stood out to you?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:00:21.935019+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/LuffyBetss/status/2036768259794427942",
      "reply_text": "PFs get a lot of looks against them. That's a good bet",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:00:56.929101+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/ApexJones22/status/2036769588206002583",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, we still bring it up. That was a tough series for him.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:01:54.055547+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/ClashPicks/status/2036774318516871564",
      "reply_text": "Thunder's streak is getting ridiculous, but Celtics' defense is no joke",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:02:30.136293+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/WOJARTESTBURNER/status/2036777458763235389",
      "reply_text": "Those dunks are still insane",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:03:21.611807+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TrashTalk_fr/status/2036754079397896290",
      "reply_text": "That's true, no unanimous DPOY in history. Ben Wallace was close in 2002, but still not unanimous.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:13:55.697229+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/JoeDellera/status/2036790957174100425",
      "reply_text": "That's true. He's been able to get his shots up against them before.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:14:28.944556+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/__LordPenguin/status/2036776295669891211",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, KD's been on fire lately, especially against the Wolves.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:15:05.140888+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/thejunglepicks/status/2036769531667120371",
      "reply_text": "Tough matchup but KD's numbers still look good",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:15:54.141560+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Nemesis3nforc3r/status/2036760973990600816",
      "reply_text": "G league stats don't translate to NBA level defense, that's a fact.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:16:40.684343+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/PolymarketHoops/status/2036788032628773252",
      "reply_text": "Brown's case is strong, but defense is a big part of MVP consideration",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:27:54.917147+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/RaptorsMuseOk/status/2036793537002447276",
      "reply_text": "Defense matters in this one.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:28:41.818370+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/KevinPorterMVP/status/2036779270026965395",
      "reply_text": "Trading Giannis is a tough pill to swallow, but it's a rebuild. KPJ's growth will be key.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:29:27.776510+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/hedgefundog/status/2036785162273407327",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, Nash's career was pure magic. Those MVPs and All-Star appearances don't lie.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:30:16.224289+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/MasterLockz/status/2036778763631968552",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, been doing that all season. No hesitation at all.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T13:30:52.389517+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/lequipe/status/2036769542416761251",
      "reply_text": "That's tough for the Grizzlies. Hope he recovers quickly.",
